INSTALLATION
    Cora can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions. Please also have a look at the file "REQUIREMENTS" for
    information on the tools required to run, compile, and develop Cora.


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of Cora. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/cora/cora.pdf>.
